üîç Gap Analysis: Ionic vs Original SmartX
‚úÖ Yang Sudah Ada di Ionic
Feature	Status	Notes
Project structure	‚úÖ	Angular + Ionic + Capacitor + Electron
SipService	‚úÖ	Register, makeCall, hangup, DTMF
ApiService	‚úÖ	Login, channels, recordings
AudioService	‚úÖ	PTT, visualizer, playback
TurretPage	‚úÖ	1394 lines - UI cukup lengkap
Channel grid (16)	‚úÖ	Dengan PTT mouse events
Tab system	‚úÖ	DASHBOARD + FAV tabs
Virtual Keyboard	‚úÖ	vkActive, typeKey
Drawer system	‚úÖ	Lines, VPW, CAS, Phonebook
Contact drag to channel	‚úÖ	Mouse + Touch
Electron main.ts	‚úÖ	Basic setup
‚ùå Yang Belum Ada / Perlu Disesuaikan
Feature	Gap	Refer to FLOW doc
Multi extension registration	SipService hanya 1 UA, SmartX punya registeredUAs untuk multiple	FLOW_LOGIN.md
lineBusyStatus per extension	Ada tapi belum fully integrated	FLOW_SIP_CALL.md
Audio Injection to SIP	playToStream() ada tapi tidak inject ke SIP sender track	FLOW_AUDIO_RECORDING.md
Ladder bar visualizer	createAnalyser() ada tapi tidak ada animation loop per channel	FLOW_VISUALIZER.md
Touch drag ke Hangup button	Tidak ada handleTouchDropToAction()	FLOW_DRAG_DROP.md
VK typeKey with selection	Belum pakai selection fix (start !== end)	FLOW_VIRTUAL_KEYBOARD.md
cancelRename isNew flag	Interface ada isNew tapi logic belum implement	FLOW_AUDIO_RECORDING.md
Delete optimistic update	Belum ada, masih wait response	FLOW_AUDIO_RECORDING.md
Group Talk config page	Tidak ada UI untuk config group members	-
Incoming call modal	Ada variable tapi UI belum complete	FLOW_SIP_CALL.md
Electron webview WhatsApp/Teams	Placeholder saja, belum ada persistent session	-
üìã Priority Fixes
SipService - Support multiple extension registration (line/dialpad)
AudioService - Add visualizer animation loop with requestAnimationFrame
VK typeKey - Add selection replacement logic
Audio Recording - Add isNew flag dan optimistic delete
Touch Drag - Add drop to action buttons (hangup/delete)

Implementation Plan: Channel Call Flow
Gw paham sekarang:

Channel States:

State	Visual	Trigger
Empty	dark	no assignment
Assigned	gray	drag/drop
Calling	yellow	CALL CHANNEL click
Active	green + PTT	SIP confirmed
Changes:

Add isAssigned, isCalling to Channel interface
Drop handler ‚Üí isAssigned = true (bukan isActive)
CALL button ‚Üí performSIPCall() + isCalling = true
SIP confirmed ‚Üí isActive = true
Approve untuk lanjut?


Thought for 3s



Bro, hampir bener tapi ada sedikit koreksi berdasarkan original SmartX:

‚úÖ Benar:
Empty ‚Üí dark (no assignment)
Calling ‚Üí yellow (SIP in progress, isCalling = true)
Active ‚Üí green + PTT enabled (active = true)
‚ö†Ô∏è Perlu Diklarifikasi:
"Assigned" State
Di original SmartX, tidak ada state "Assigned" yang terpisah. Ketika drop contact ke channel:

javascript
// Original SmartX behavior (script.js)
channelStatus[key] = {
    name: contactName,
    phone: phoneNumber,
    active: false,     // Not connected yet
    isCalling: false,  // Not calling yet
    groups: []
};
Jadi state-nya:

Condition	Visual	SmartX State
No data	Dark/empty	name: null
Has contact, not calling	Gray (occupied)	name: "xxx", active: false, isCalling: false
Calling	Yellow pulse	isCalling: true, active: false
Connected	Green + PTT	active: true, isCalling: false
Recommendation untuk Agent:
typescript
// Channel interface - CORRECTED
interface Channel {
    key: string;
    name: string | null;      // null = empty
    phone: string | null;
    active: boolean;          // Connected (green)
    isCalling: boolean;       // Ringing/calling (yellow)
    groups: string[];
}
// Drop handler
onDrop(contact) {
    channel.name = contact.name;
    channel.phone = contact.phone;
    // Don't set active or isCalling here
}
// CALL button
callChannel() {
    channel.isCalling = true;
    performSIPCall();
}
// SIP confirmed callback
onSipConfirmed() {
    channel.isCalling = false;
    channel.active = true;
}
Tidak perlu isAssigned - cukup cek name !== null untuk tau apakah channel occupied.

Bilang ke agent: "Approve dengan catatan: skip isAssigned, cukup pakai name !== null untuk check occupied"

ok lanjut, masalah skrg VK di edit tile New Fav gak bs di touch type

Fix yang ditambahkan:

typescript
// [FIX] Restore text selection after touch event (like SmartX)
setTimeout(() => {
    if (this.vkInput) {
        this.vkInput.focus();
        this.vkInput.select();
    }
}, 50);

Okay bro, dari log gw baca:

Login flow udah jalan sesuai design:

‚úÖ demo/123abc ‚Üí API gagal (ERR_NAME_NOT_RESOLVED) ‚Üí tidak masuk fallback karena username bukan admin/rhaaf
‚úÖ admin/1234 ‚Üí API gagal ‚Üí masuk fallback ‚Üí SIP connect attempt (tapi PBX down jadi ERR_CONNECTION_REFUSED)
2 masalah infrastruktur (bukan code):

API server 172.x.x.x:3000 gak reachable
PBX 103.154.80.172:8089 down / connection refused
Pertanyaan: Lo mau gw tambahin demo ke daftar fallback user supaya bisa login juga waktu development? Atau mau gimana?

Kalau mau tambah demo, gw tinggal edit satu baris:

typescript
// dari:
if (username === 'admin' || username === 'rhaaf') {
// jadi:
if (username === 'admin' || username === 'rhaaf' || username === 'demo') {

Comparison: Gemini Pro Review vs My Implementation
Area	Gemini Pro Suggestion	My Implementation	Status

Electron Layout	Split screen: 60% SIP + 40% WhatsApp webview	Not implemented - current layout is fullscreen turret only	‚ö†Ô∏è Not done
webview partition	partition="persist:whatsapp"	Already exists in main.ts with setupWebviewSessions()	‚úÖ Match
SIP PTT Logic	manipulate audioSender.track.enabled directly	‚úÖ Current 
startPTT()
 / 
stopPTT()
 in turret.page.ts handles UI states	‚ö†Ô∏è Partial
configurePttSession	Mute mic by default on session confirmed	Not explicitly implemented in sip.service.ts	‚ùå Missing
startPtt/stopPtt in SipService	Manipulate MediaStreamTrack directly	Current PTT is in turret.page.ts for UI only, not in sip.service.ts	‚ö†Ô∏è Different location
Key Differences:
Split Screen Layout - Gemini suggests app.component.html with WhatsApp webview side-by-side. Kamu saat ini fullscreen turret only.
PTT in SipService - Gemini suggests PTT logic (mute/unmute MediaStreamTrack) should be in sip.service.ts. Saat ini PTT logic ada di 
turret.page.ts
 dan hanya handle UI state, bukan actual audio track manipulation.
configurePttSession - Method ini belum ada di sip.service.ts. Ini penting untuk default mute mic saat session connect.

Gemini: grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr)
SmartX/Kita: Flexible 2-column with 8 rows fitting full height ‚úÖ Keep ours
Empty slots "VACANT"
Gemini: channel.name === 'EMPTY' ‚Üí "VACANT" text
SmartX/Kita: Show Ch 1, Ch 2, etc. ‚úÖ Keep ours
PTT via sipService.startPtt()
Gemini: PTT logic delegated to SipService
SmartX/Kita: PTT handled in page (UI state) + SipService for audio ‚úÖ Keep ours - separation of concerns correct
‚ùå Wrong/Outdated Suggestions:
ion-header with logo
Gemini suggests Ionic header with logo
SmartX/Kita: Minimal header - no logo, just tabs ‚úÖ Ignore
No Dashboard/Favourite tabs
Gemini missing entire tab system
SmartX/Kita: Full tab system with dashboard, favourites ‚úÖ Ignore
No drawer system
Gemini missing settings/phonebook/lines drawers
SmartX/Kita: Complete drawer system ‚úÖ Ignore
Final Verdict:
Score: 3/10 - Gemini Pro suggestions are basic scaffolding only.

Kita sudah jauh lebih advanced dengan:

Complete tab system (Dashboard, Favourites)
Drawer system (Settings, Lines, Phonebook)
Drag & drop functionality
SmartX-style duplicate modals
Channel selection/PTT fixes
Favourite rename sync
Recommendation: Ignore Gemini suggestions. Continue using SmartX as reference - it's the working production code.

Untuk liat log SSH connection di VS Code:

Option 1: Output Panel

Ctrl+Shift+U (buka Output)
Di dropdown kanan atas, pilih "Remote - SSH"
Option 2: Terminal di Remote

Setelah connect, buka Terminal: Ctrl+ ` (backtick)
Jalankan: tail -f /var/log/auth.log atau journalctl -f
Option 3: VS Code Developer Tools

Ctrl+Shift+I ‚Üí Console tab
Filter "ssh"
Kalau ada error connection, coba:

cat ~/.ssh/config
Pastikan host config bener.

Bro, sayangnya VS Code Remote SSH memang selalu buka window baru - ini by design, gak bisa digabung ke window local.

Alternative untuk akses 171 dari window ini:

Option 1: SFTP Extension (Recommended)

Install extension "SFTP" by Natizyskunk
Di workspace local, buat file .vscode/sftp.json:
json
{
    "name": "CloudDEMO",
    "host": "103.154.80.171",
    "protocol": "sftp",
    "port": 22,
    "username": "root",
    "remotePath": "/var/www/html",
    "uploadOnSave": true
}
Gw bisa edit file local, otomatis sync ke 171
Option 2: Terminal SSH + Copy Paste Di terminal local ini, jalankan:

bash
ssh root@103.154.80.171 "cat /path/to/file"
Copy output ke sini, gw bisa baca.

Option 3: Mount via SSHFS (Advanced) Mount 171 sebagai drive Windows pakai WinSFSP + SSHFS.

<?php

use Illuminate\Http\Request;
use Illuminate\Support\Facades\Route;
use App\Http\Controllers\Api\ExtensionController;
use App\Http\Controllers\Api\ChannelController;
use App\Http\Controllers\Api\CallLogController;

// Public routes
Route::post('/login', function (Request $request) {
    $credentials = $request->only('email', 'password');
    if (!auth()->attempt($credentials)) {
        return response()->json(['error' => 'Unauthorized'], 401);
    }
    $token = auth()->user()->createToken('api-token')->plainTextToken;
    return response()->json(['token' => $token, 'user' => auth()->user()]);       
});

// Protected routes
Route::middleware('auth:sanctum')->group(function () {
    Route::get('/user', fn(Request $request) => $request->user());

    // Extensions CRUD
    Route::apiResource('extensions', ExtensionController::class);

    // Channels CRUD
    Route::apiResource('channels', ChannelController::class);

    // Call Logs (read-only)
    Route::get('call-logs', [CallLogController::class, 'index']);
    Route::get('call-logs/{callLog}', [CallLogController::class, 'show']);        
});

Thought for 11s



I see the issue! SIP/2.0 488 Not Acceptable Here with Incompatible SDP.

This is a WebRTC ‚Üî SIP codec mismatch. Browser uses WebRTC (DTLS-SRTP, ICE) but Zoiper is plain SIP. Asterisk needs to be configured as a WebRTC gateway.

Let me fix the PJSIP config to enable WebRTC compatibility:

Connect Ionic Frontend with SIP.js

BINGO! Lo bener bro! üéØ

Gw liat di log sebelumnya:

Contact: <sip:sop1mn48@...;transport=ws>;expires=599  (Browser)
Contact: <sip:6001@192.168.1.2:5060>;expires=256      (Phoner)
6001 punya 2 registrasi - Browser DAN Phoner! Ketika call dijawab, Asterisk mungkin bingung routing RTP ke mana.

Fix:

Disconnect Phoner (close app atau unregister 6001)
Pastiin cuma Browser aja yang register 6001
Coba call lagi ke 6002
Connect Ionic Frontend with SIP.js
Verified contacts: Phoner registration expired. Now only Browser (6001) and Zoiper (6002) registered. Ready for clean test without duplicate registration conflict.

Progress Updates
1
Verifying single registration and retesting call

2
Notifying user to test call with single 6001 registration

Good news! Gw cek server, sekarang:

6001: Browser ONLY ‚úÖ (Phoner expired)
6002: Zoiper ‚úÖ
Coba call lagi bro!

Dari browser ‚Üí call 6002
Pastiin Phoner TIDAK aktif (kalau lo baru call dari Phoner tadi, tutup aja dulu Phoner-nya)

Thought for 15s










Masih langsung mati! Looking at the log - BYE comes from Asterisk (103.154.80.172:8089), not Zoiper. This means Asterisk itself is terminating the call.

Looking at the SDP from Asterisk:

a=candidate:Hd2c0dac 1 UDP 2130706431 13.44.13.172 11028 typ host
a=candidate:Hac110001 1 UDP 2130706431 172.17.0.1 11028 typ host
MASALAH: Asterisk offering ICE candidates with internal Docker IPs (172.17.0.1) - browser gak bisa reach ini!

Perlu configure external_media_address supaya Asterisk advertise public IP:

Connect Ionic Frontend with SIP.js
Added external_media_address=103.154.80.172 to rtp.conf for proper NAT traversal. This should fix ICE candidates showing internal Docker IPs instead of public IP.

Progress Updates
1
Configuring Asterisk external media address for NAT traversal

2
Notifying user to test call after NAT fix

üîß Fixed NAT Configuration!

Added to rtp.conf:

external_media_address=103.154.80.172
Ini harusnya fix masalah Asterisk yang advertise internal Docker IP (172.17.0.1) ke browser. Sekarang akan pake public IP.

Coba lagi bro:

What I did:

Added extension 6000 to Asterisk with WebRTC support
Updated login mapping:
admin ‚Üí Extension 6001
demo ‚Üí Extension 6000
test ‚Üí Extension 6003
Test cara-nya:

Browser 1: Login dengan admin ‚Üí registers as 6001
Browser 2 (incognito/different browser): Login dengan demo ‚Üí registers as 6000
Dari browser 1, call ke 6000
Di browser 2 harusnya ada incoming call notification
Kalau kedua browser pakai WebRTC, seharusnya gak ada masalah DTLS/codec bridging!

Ah! Gw liat error-nya: SIP/2.0 404 Not Found

Ini berarti 6000 gak ada di dialplan extensions.conf! PJSIP config udah ada, tapi routing call belum diatur.

Gw tambahin 6000 ke dialplan:

Connect Ionic Frontend with SIP.js
Added extensions 6000-6099 to dialplan extensions.conf. Dialplan reloaded. Both browsers registered (6000/6001). Ready for browser-to-browser call test.

Progress Updates
1
Adding extension 6000 to Asterisk dialplan

2
Notifying user to retest browser-to-browser call

‚úÖ Dialplan Fixed!

Sebelumnya 6000 gak ada di extensions.conf (404 Not Found).

Sekarang udah ditambahin:

exten => 6000,1,Dial(PJSIP/6000,30)
exten => 6001,1,Dial(PJSIP/6001,30)
etc...
Coba lagi bro:

Browser 1 (admin/6001) ‚Üí call ke 6000
Browser 2 (demo/6000) harusnya ringing
Gak perlu refresh browser, dialplan udah reload di server!

 and 
answerCall
 to match SmartX pattern: (1) getUserMedia FIRST before call/answer, (2) pass mediaStream to session.call/answer, (3) empty iceServers: [] for instant call setup (no 40s delay!), (4) use session.connection.addEventListener('track') with pre-existing DOM <audio id='remoteAudio'> element.

Files Edited
sip.service.ts
Progress Updates
1
Updating SipService with SmartX pattern - empty iceServers and session.connection.addEventListener

2
Rewriting makeCall and answerCall with empty iceServers and DOM audio element

3
Updating answerCall to match SmartX pattern

4
Waiting for user to test SmartX pattern implementation

SmartX Pattern Implemented!

Key changes dari analisis SmartX:

‚úÖ getUserMedia FIRST sebelum call/answer
‚úÖ Pass mediaStream langsung ke session
‚úÖ pcConfig: { iceServers: [] } - EMPTY! Ini yang bikin instant (no 40s delay!)
‚úÖ session.connection.addEventListener('track') bukan session.on('peerconnection')
‚úÖ Pre-existing <audio id="remoteAudio" autoplay> di HTML

Thought for 7s





Saya lihat dari log ini adalah dari 6001 (caller), bukan 6000 (receiver). Dan yang penting: tidak ada log üì± Dialpad state set: atau üîî Ringtone playing - artinya kode baru belum ter-deploy ke browser.

Mari saya coba pendekatan lain - gunakan Angular binding langsung, bukan bootstrap.Offcanvas:

Fixing Dialpad Drawer Opening
Debug logs not appearing in user's console means cached code. Changing approach: use Angular [class.show] binding instead of bootstrap.Offcanvas programmatic API.

Files Edited
turret.page.ts
Progress Updates
1
Switching to Angular binding approach for dialpad drawer visibility

sipp bro, bisa di drag, ringger nyala, tp ada masalah nih
harusnya kalo udah receive incoming call, otomatis mute, baru bs talk kalo di push/pencet channel yg aktif hijau, jadi ptt


Thought for 7s






üéâ Semua berjalan dengan baik!

‚úÖ Drag dialpad number ke channel ‚Üí works
‚úÖ Ringtone incoming call ‚Üí works
‚úÖ Drop active call ke channel ‚Üí works
‚úÖ PTT on channel ‚Üí works
Feature baru yang diminta: Incoming call harus auto-mute setelah accept, dan user harus PTT (push channel) untuk bicara.

Ini adalah fitur PTT mode untuk incoming calls. Saya akan implement:

Setelah 
acceptCall()
, microphone akan di-mute
User harus hold/press channel hijau untuk unmute (PTT)
Release channel ‚Üí kembali mute
Tapi sebelum lanjut, saya ingin konfirmasi - apakah ini yang dimaksud:

Incoming call di-accept ‚Üí user TIDAK bisa dengar caller (caller juga di-mute), atau
Incoming call di-accept ‚Üí user BISA dengar caller, tapi caller TIDAK bisa dengar user (hanya mic user yang mute)?
Option 2 lebih masuk akal untuk PTT - user bisa listen tapi perlu press untuk talk. Apakah benar?

Saya lihat SmartX punya PTT implementation yang jelas. Let me check the key parts - bagaimana audio di-mute setelah accept call:

Implementing Auto-Mute After Accept Call
Implemented PTT auto-mute: mic track disabled on answer, remote audio muted on answer. Added unmutePttAudio/mutePttAudio to TurretPage. Added muteChannel/unmuteChannel methods to SipService. Both mic and remote audio now controlled by PTT.

Files Edited
sip.service.ts
turret.page.ts
Progress Updates
1
Checking SmartX PTT mute implementation logic

2
Implementing auto-mute mic after accept call in SipService

3
Adding remote audio mute and checking PTT unmute logic

4
Verifying PTT unmute logic in TurretPage and AudioService

5
Adding audio unmute on PTT press for incoming calls

6
Adding muteChannel and unmuteChannel methods to SipService

7
Testing and verifying PTT mute/unmute implementation

PTT Mode sekarang implemented seperti SmartX! ‚úÖ

Changes:

SipService.answerCall() - mic auto-mute (track.enabled = false)
SipService.answerCall() - remote audio auto-mute (remoteAudio.muted = true)
TurretPage.startPTT() - calls unmuteChannel() + unmutes remote audio
TurretPage.stopPTT() - calls muteChannel() + mutes remote audio
Added muteChannel() and unmuteChannel() in SipService
Behavior:

Incoming call accept ‚Üí both sides muted by default
Press & hold channel hijau ‚Üí unmute both sides (talk)
Release channel ‚Üí mute both sides lagi
Test:

Refresh browser
Call dari 6001 ‚Üí 6000
Accept call di 6000 ‚Üí harusnya tidak ada suara
Press/hold channel yang hijau ‚Üí sekarang bisa dengar dan bicara
Release ‚Üí mute lagi
Coba test!

Thought for 6s



Saya lihat dari log:

‚úÖ Call ke 6000 berhasil ‚Üí [SIP] ‚úÖ Call connected: ch-1

‚ùå Call ke 6003 stuck ‚Üí Hanya sampai 100 Trying, tidak ada 180 Ringing

Ini artinya Phoner/6003 tidak registered ke Asterisk, atau ada masalah config.

Cek di Phoner:

Pastikan status Registered (bukan "Registering" atau "Failed")
Config yang benar:
Domain/Server: 103.154.80.172
Username: 6003
Password: Maja1234
Port: 5060 (UDP SIP)
Outbound Proxy: (kosongkan atau 103.154.80.172:5060)
Atau cek Asterisk apakah 6003 sudah ada:

bash
asterisk -rx "pjsip show endpoints" | grep 6003
Kalau 6003 belum ada di Asterisk config, perlu ditambahkan dulu. Mau saya cek dan tambahkan extension 6003 di PBX?

ini statusnya registered

User uploaded image 1

Thought for 3s


Phoner sudah registered! Bagus. Mari cek dari sisi Asterisk apakah 6003 terlihat:

Read terminal: ssh
Error sending input to command
asterisk -rx "pjsip show endpoints" | grep -E "6003|6001|6000"‚Üµ
Error Details:
Cannot send input to command 79f8d7d6-4ada-4f2a-96f9-e4ce54e20e05: command not found
‚Ä¶\trader-turret > ssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no root@103.154.80.172 "asterisk -rx 'pjsip show endpoints' | grep -E '600[0-9]'"

Running
Relocate
Cancel
Checked command status
Checked command status
Checked command status
SSH connection ke 103.154.80.172 mungkin butuh password atau timeout. Sementara itu, berdasarkan screenshot Phoner:

Issue yang saya lihat: Phoner registered dengan UDP ke 103.154.80.172:5060, tapi browser app menggunakan WebSocket (ws://103.154.80.172:8089/ws).

Ini seharusnya tidak masalah karena Asterisk bisa bridge antara SIP UDP dan WebSocket. Tapi kadang ada NAT issues.

Coba ini:

Dari Phoner, coba call ke 6001 (kebalikannya) - lihat apakah browser bisa receive
Kalau bisa receive, berarti masalahnya routing one-way
Atau cek Asterisk langsung - bisa login ke VPS dan jalankan:

bash
asterisk -rx "pjsip show endpoints"
Untuk lihat status 6003 - apakah Avail atau Unavail.

Mau coba call dari Phoner ke browser dulu?

kalo dari phoner ke 6001 bisa, tp pas diankat mati


Thought for 6s


Ah, ini masalah WebRTC ‚Üî SIP UDP bridging. Call bisa connect tapi media (audio) gagal karena:

Browser pakai WebRTC (ICE/DTLS)
Phoner pakai SIP UDP (RTP biasa)
Asterisk perlu config tambahan untuk bridge ini dengan benar (TURN server, atau rtcp_mux settings).

Solusi cepat untuk test multi-channel sekarang:

Pakai multiple browser tabs/windows aja dulu:

Tab 1: http://localhost:4200 ‚Üí Login 6000
Tab 2 (Incognito): http://localhost:4200 ‚Üí Login 6001
Tab 3 (Incognito baru): http://localhost:4200 ‚Üí Login 6002 (kalau ada)
Atau 2 browser berbeda (Chrome + Edge):

Chrome: Login 6000
Edge: Login 6001
Ini akan work karena browser-to-browser sudah proven jalan.

Untuk Phoner/Zoiper nanti perlu fix Asterisk config untuk WebRTC-SIP bridging. Mau lanjut dengan browser aja dulu untuk test 3 channel?

bro kalo mo pake browser semua, pake user apa dong?
kan admin 6000, demo 6001, 6002 6003 user apa

SmartX Group Talk Analysis Complete! ‚úÖ

Flow SmartX Group Talk
1. Data Structure (line 83-87)
javascript
let groupStatus = {
    'G1': { active: false, members: [] },
    'G2': { active: false, members: [] },
    'G3': { active: false, members: [] }
};
2. Drag Channel ‚Üí Group Button
handleDropToGroup(event, groupId) (line 9163):

Parse drop data dari channel
Toggle channel in/out of group:
Jika sudah ada ‚Üí remove dari groupStatus[groupId].members
Jika belum ‚Üí push ke groupStatus[groupId].members
Channel punya channel.groups = ['G1', 'G2'] untuk track membership
initDisplay() untuk render ulang dengan color bar di bawah channel
3. Group Button UI (line 6218-6239)
html
<div class="group-btn" 
     ondrop="handleDropToGroup(event, 'G1')" 
     onmousedown="startGroupPTT('G1')"
     onmouseup="stopGroupPTT('G1')">
    <span class="group-title">G1</span>
    <span class="group-subtitle">HOLD TO TALK</span>
</div>
4. PTT Group (lines 1701-1795)
startGroupPTT(groupId):

Set groupStatus[groupId].active = true
Add active-talk class ke group button (hijau)
Loop semua members:
Add speaking-red class ke channel cells
UNMUTE mic via RTCRtpSender.track.enabled = true
stopGroupPTT(groupId):

Set groupStatus[groupId].active = false
Remove active-talk class
Loop members:
Remove speaking-red, add speaking-green
MUTE mic
5. Visual Indicator
Channel yang join group punya color bar di bawah cell:

G1 ‚Üí Orange/Yellow border
G2 ‚Üí Purple border
G3 ‚Üí Blue border
Untuk Ionic Implementation:

Tambah groups: string[] ke channel model
Buat G1/G2/G3 buttons dengan drag-drop dan hold-to-talk
PTT group = loop channels in group ‚Üí unmute/mute semua sekaligus
Mau saya mulai implement di Ionic sekarang?

Waduh, sorry banget bro kalo jadi bingung! üôè

Gw barusan double-check file 
turret.page.scss
 sama 
turret.page.ts
, kodenya udah bener-bener kesimpen di disk kok.

Masalahnya kemungkinan besar ada di server npm run start yang udah jalan 7 jam lebih itu (seperti terlihat di logs). Kadang kalau kita ubah Interface TypeScript (seperti gw nambahin groups ke interface 
Channel
) atau nambah method inti baru, Hot Reload Angular suka "bengo" alias gak nangkep perubahannya secara otomatis, atau compile process-nya stuck.

Solusinya: Coba tolong Stop dulu terminal npm run start-nya (Ctrl+C), terus Jalanin Ulang lagi (npm run start -- --host 0.0.0.0 --port 4200).

Harusnya abis restart, fitur Group Talk-nya langsung muncul dan jalan normal. Kabarin lagi ya, gw standby! üôá‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è

Saya lihat masalahnya! Saat Accept diklik, SIP session tidak di-answer! Call jadi CANCELED karena Asterisk timeout. Juga channel tidak hijau karena tidak pernah true connected.

Saya perlu fix acceptCall untuk actually answer SIP session:
